description: The theme for the weekend was "To be one with Christ". Christ desire for his disciples and for us is to be one with him. The bible says in John 17:11 "And now I am no more in the world, but these are in the world, and I come to thee. Holy Father, keep through thine own name those whom thou hast given me, that they may be one, as we are".
